entries.femaleVariant: You heard? James' brother just retired.
No. Japantown. Casino. Everyone's saying he had a runner helpin' him, but I dunno. Prolly just a rumor.
Still damn lucky. What's he gonna do with all that cash?
Apparently goin' to… where was it? Sicily? Some place called Modica.
Ha ha, how the hell should I know? Just said some shit about his great-grandpa or someone bein' from there…
